Audio Countdown - Count down with audio and text toggle
-------------------------------------------------------

The countdown with a play, pause button and audio is easy to use when you only need one audio element in your website. Your audio starts when you click Play and pauses itself. When you click on "Toon tekst" there will be a block with text fade.

* Easy to use
* Minimal css
* Customizable


Build with
----------
* Html5
* css3
* Javascript


Contents
--------
	- Packages
		- Index.html
		- Css map
			style.css
		- Js map
			javascript.js
